        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="70" name="Message" rows="12" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
Thought this would be a very funny/interesting topic, and I will start off with me.

1. Went to Toxx forest when I was lvl 8, and saw this ogre, and he cast a spell on me. Next thing I knew was my monitor went completely blank, and I resetted my computer, hoping it would fix my monitor. Well I went after the same ogre, and it did it again. Little did I know there was a spell called Blind   =)  DUHHHHHHHHH Stupid Noob

2. When I hit Lvl 4 (DING) I was leaving Paineel, and I saw these 2 wood elfs named Micky LvL28 and Minnie Lvl30 outside our rock door. Well I thought I would be really cool and Impress these HIGH lvl people. Well I asked them if they had ever been to Paineel. They hadnt so I thought I would show them the place. Well I didnt know about faction. Well they went down there with me, and immediatley the guards attacked them. So I thought I would save there asses and get the elevator up, well I did and one ran straight into the HOLE, and had to wait for about 2 hours for someone to get his bod.  



I cant wait to read some of these

 
